---
title: Beef & Veggie Ragu with Gnocchi with Mexican Beef Chilli Rice Bowl for Lunch
description: Cook once, with a twist for lunch. Cook an amazing dinner as usual, then create a new twist on the recipe to create
something different for lunch the next day! Start with an Italian beef ragu with pan-fried gnocchi, then add a little
spice to your beef mixture and turn it into a Mexican chilli to enjoy with rice for lunch. Extra delicious!

